            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The name of the emperor has been erased because of the damnatio memoriae, but actually it is still possible to read it. (B): Walser 1994: Z. 1-2: [M(arco)] / [[Aur(elio) Caro]]; Rosso: Z. 4: tri[bunicia po]; Z. 5: t[estate].</p>
